Please try my fix for this problem
https://github.com/darkdef/yii2/commit/016220f7837fc381066136c57c6929c2c66d95d5

Hi @darkdef 

this fix seems to work. The resulting query only selects the primary key values:

```sql
SET NOCOUNT ON;
DECLARE @temporary_inserted TABLE ([id] int);
INSERT INTO [user] (...)
    OUTPUT INSERTED.id INTO @temporary_inserted
    VALUES (...);
SELECT * FROM @temporary_inserted
```
